system-info-description =
    A live system resource monitor widget for the FreeSynergy desktop.

    Shows CPU utilization per core, RAM and swap usage, disk space for the primary
    volume, and network upload/download throughput. Data is sourced from the fs-sysinfo
    crate running inside FreeSynergy Node and updated every second.

system-info-features =
    - Live CPU utilization per core
    - RAM and swap usage with bar graph
    - Disk space for the primary volume
    - Network upload and download throughput
    - 1-second refresh rate
    - Compact and expandable layout
